!item [Syntax:]
int16_t edit_get_colour ( OBJECT *tree, int16_t obj, 
                       int16_t *tcolour, int16_t  *bcolour );

!item [Description:]
The call edit_get_colour obtains the colour of an object. The following apply:
               
